Class User

java.lang.Object
entities.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AreaManager, RegisteredCustomer
public class User extends Object implements Serializable
This class is the User entity which hold all the information of the User entity with getters and setters for each attribute, correspond to the 'user' table in database
